transcripts.text: This is their new hoax.  We have it totally under control.  It's one person coming in from China.

One day it's like a miracle.  It will disappear.  When you have 15 people and within a couple of days it's going to be down to close to zero, we really think we've done a great job in keeping it down to a minimum.  I like this stuff.  I really get it.  People are surprised that I understand it.  No, I don't take responsibility at all.
